name: Remove rounded corners on Google
description: Google Search added rounded corners to fit in with the new Google Chrome design. This stylesheet reverts the corners back to how they used to be. You can change the preferred border-radius in the style settings.
additional_info:
Currently styled Google products
- Google Search
- Google Images
- Google News
- Google Account
- Google Drive
- Google Support
- Google Takeout
- Google Keep


Github: https://github.com/SydLambert/stylus-remove-rounded-corners

style_setting_options.label: Enabled
